<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Liquid Glass Blob — Gaming Site Demo</title>
<style>
  /* ============================================================
     DEMO PAGE STYLES — this part is just to showcase the widget.
     Your real site already has its own layout/CSS — ignore this.
     ============================================================ */
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #16161a;
