</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero-section" data-blob-hint="home">
  <div class="eyebrow">Nexus Arena · Gaming Platform Demo</div>
  <h1>Scroll around.<br>The blob is watching.</h1>
  <p>This page exists to show off the floating assistant in the corner. It drifts on its own, reacts to what section you're reading, and turns into a full chat panel when you tap it. Everything runs locally in the browser — no server, no API key, works offline.</p>
</section>

<section data-blob-hint="library">
  <div class="eyebrow">Game Library</div>
  <h1>200+ titles, one launcher.</h1>
  <p>From competitive shooters to cozy sims. Ask the blob for system requirements, download help, or install issues once you open the chat.</p>
</section>

<section data-blob-hint="tournaments">
  <div class="eyebrow">Tournaments</div>
  <h1>Ranked ladders every season.</h1>
  <p>Ask about matchmaking, ranks, or how to register a team.</p>
</section>

<section data-blob-hint="store">
  <div class="eyebrow">Store</div>
  <h1>Simple, fair pricing.</h1>
  <p>Ask the blob about subscriptions, refunds, or payment methods.</p>
</section>

<section data-blob-hint="support">
  <div class="eyebrow">Support</div>
  <h1>Talk to a human, or the blob.</h1>
  <p>Either works. The blob is faster to reach at 3am.</p>
</section>

