      support: "Need a real fix fast? Tap me — I know the common issues."
    },
    /* ============================================================
       KNOWLEDGE BASE — offline, rule-based Q&A for a gaming site.
       Each entry: keywords (any match triggers it) + reply.
       Add/edit freely — first match wins, so put specific
